  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>RepairQ includes a powerful Business Intelligence (BI) Suite, provided through integration with Looker. This tool offers a set of visual dashboards covering key performance indicators (KPIs) essential for running a retail repair business. These reports allow you to quickly view important aspects of your business, such as sales trends, inventory levels, and repair progress, helping you make more informed decisions.</p><p>Our Business Intelligence (BI) Dashboards are available to Admin users on our Advanced and Professional plans. Users on the <strong>Advanced Plan</strong> can view a wide range of pre-built reports and dashboards, giving them access to critical insights about their business. However, they are limited to viewing these pre-made reports and cannot create new ones. <strong>Professional Plan</strong> users can view pre-built reports and build custom reports. This allows them to tailor reports to their specific needs and gain deeper insights from their data.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Control - f79824.png\" width=\"760\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/2731114524/Control%20-%20f79824.png?api=v2\"></span><ul><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1936785446\" rel=\"nofollow\">Business Intelligence - Analytics Dashboards</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1936621637\" rel=\"nofollow\">Analytics Dashboards - Explore and Download Data</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2738651142\" rel=\"nofollow\">Business Intelligence - Create a Report</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1937670188\" rel=\"nofollow\">Business Intelligence - Inventory Forecasting</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1936392337\" rel=\"nofollow\">Business Intelligence - Troubleshooting</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/1937014890\" rel=\"nofollow\">Automate Customer List Exports to Mailchimp via Zapier</a></p></li><li><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/9/article/2471034883\" rel=\"nofollow\">Integrations: Webhooks and APIs</a></p></li></ul><p />",
